# Local state (user projects get their own .omao/)
.omao-local/
.claude/settings.local.json

# OMA runtime state — PII, verbatim prompts, approval logs, cost data.
# audit-trail captures user input verbatim (SOC2/ISMS-P retention);
# incident-response stores alarm payloads (may include account IDs, ARNs);
# cost dirs hold per-agent Cost Explorer exports and override overrides.
# Never commit. `.omao/triggers.json` is intentionally tracked as a
# distributable asset, so we ignore subdirs selectively rather than all of .omao/.
.omao/state/
.omao/plans/
.omao/logs/
.omao/notepad.md
.omao/project-memory.json
.omao/research/
**/.omao/state/
**/.omao/plans/
**/.omao/logs/

# OMC runtime state (session-specific, never committed)
.omc/
**/.omc/

# Test fixtures
evals/_runs/

# Claude Code plugin manifest (local only)
.claude-plugin/

# (Previously ignored .github/workflows/ while mirroring to GitLab.
# Now published via aws-samples on GitHub — workflows are tracked.)

# CLAUDE.md is local-only per top-level rule in CLAUDE.md; never tracked
CLAUDE.md
**/CLAUDE.md
